attachments.title: Portland Women Who Tech, Code & Hack Holiday Party
attachments.text: Portland Women who Tech, Code and Hack Holiday Party What: Come enjoy a snack and drink and celebrate the holidays with other Portland women in technology!  Network, learn about all the groups serving women in computing and technology in PDX, and hatch fun plans for future collaborations! When: Thursday, Dec. 11 from 5-8pm Where: West Cafe - 1201 SW Jefferson St, Portland, OR 97201 Join with us: ChickTech Code Scouts Girl Develop It PDX Lesbians who Tech PDX PDX Women in Tech Pyladies PDX Women who Code Women who Hack                     We are grateful to our sponsors: Gold Sponsor: Thanks to our host:
attachments.fallback: Eventbrite: Portland Women Who Tech, Code &amp; Hack Holiday Party
